{
  "page": "Lhazar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Lhazar is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Lhazar is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 67.8%; left: 76.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Lhazar\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Lhazar</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the location of Lhazar\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Lhazar</b> is an area of the semi-arid lands south of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>. A region of pastures and hills, it is inhabited by the <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazareen\" title=\"Lhazareen\">Lhazareen</a>, a people of sheep herders, and in the southern parts by <a href=\"/index.php/Ghis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ghis\">Ghiscari</a>. There are three cities in Lhazar, <a href=\"/index.php/Hesh\" title=\"Hesh\">Hesh</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazosh\" title=\"Lhazosh\">Lhazosh</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Kosrak\" title=\"Kosrak\">Kosrak</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Skahazadhan\" title=\"Skahazadhan\">Skahazadhan</a> passes through northern Lhazar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lhazar borders the Dothraki sea to the north and <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> to the south. It is connected to <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> via the <a href=\"/index.php/Khyzai_Pass\" title=\"Khyzai Pass\">Khyzai Pass</a> in the sandstone mountains.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lhazar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Beyond the hills lies Lhazar. The <a href=\"/index.php/Lhazareen\" title=\"Lhazareen\">Lamb Men</a>, as your <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> call them, a notably unwarlike people.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lhazar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_the_dothraki_sea.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  The Dothraki Sea.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:tran